

Risk scoring
1. Take all the transactions this user is a buyer or a seller, aggregate the counts of completed and disputed
    user => { 'completed': 8, 'disputed': 2 }  success = 80%, risk = 20%  (2/(8+2) = 0.2 * 100 = 20%)



